snippet.textDisplay:
Whoever did the English subtitles for this video clearly can't understand Portuguese. What he actually said was:

"It's hard to find words to describe what I have been through here. I would like to think I've left my mark on this amazing club, but now I need to set myself a new challenge away from Sporting. As sad as I am to be leaving, I know it's for the best, personally. The fans will always be in my heart and I will never forget all the amazing moments we shared over the years. Looking ahead, I am excited to be joining my new teammates. Hopefully I will fit in well there. Manchester is a beautiful city with a lot of culture and I can't wait to win trophies with one of the modern greats in management. (Indistinct talking from behind the camera). What do you mean I'm not going to City? (Tears begin to roll)".

You're welcome 👍🏻
